=== Qualifying classification ===

*Positions in red indicate entries that failed to qualify.

== Race ==

=== Classification ===
== Notes ==

* This was the 5th pole position set by a French driver.
* This was the 10th Grand Prix start for a Finnish driver.
* This was the 1st Grand Prix win for a Canadian driver.
* This was also the 300th Grand Prix start for a British driver. In those 300 races, British drivers had won 112 Grands Prix, achieved 255 podium finishes, 114 pole positions, 104 fastest laps, 28 Grand Slams and won 10 World Championships.

