* &quot;The Way of a Pilgrim, and The Pilgrim Continues His Way&quot; (1978) Helen Bacovcin (translator), Walter Ciszek (foreword), Image Doubleday 1985 reprint: 
* &quot;The Way of a Pilgrim and A Pilgrim Continues His Way&quot; (1991) Olga Savin (translator), Thomas Hopko (foreword), Shambhala 2001 reprint: 
* &quot;The Pilgrim&#x27;s Tale&quot; (1999) edited and with an introduction by Aleksei Pentkovsky, T. Allan Smith (translator), Jaroslav Pelikan (preface), Paulist Press, 
* &quot;The Way of a Pilgrim&quot; (2001) abridged translation and annotation on facing pages by Gleb Pokrovsky, Skylight Paths, 
* &quot;The Way of a Pilgrim: Candid Tales of a Wanderer to His Spiritual Father&quot; (2017), Anna Zaranko (translator), Andrew Louth (introduction), Penguin Books, 

